rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0001
rows.name: I confess...you were right about one thing:[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0002
rows.name: I was indeed fearful of humanity, of your threat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0003
rows.name:
At the dawn of the cosmos,
the Samaarians arrived from another plane.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0004
rows.name: We Ganglion are forbidden from turning against them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0005
rows.name:
If we ever tried, we would be destroyed.
I thought that it was just a myth...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0006
rows.name: And yet, here you are. The descendants of Samaar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0008
rows.name:
How could YOU be their legacy?
Such a primitive people. Barbaric![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070180_MSG0009
rows.name:
And yet the stories would have us bow down before you?
NEVER![ST:wait ]
